    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>People who create conceptual schemes for the organization or appearance of lighting for theater, television, or film productions using color, form, surface, and space to create a visual language capable of communicating ideas relevant to the production.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
